# Force LF for the scaffold's OWN files (incl template/*.jinja) so copier always renders LF and the
# E2E ruff-format gate is platform-independent. (Generated projects get their own .gitattributes.)
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary

# Generated but TRACKED — dogfood the same rules the template ships (see template/.gitattributes for the
# three-tier rationale). tier 1 = beads state (line file, wholesale re-export, never hand-read → hide +
# union); tier 3 = archmap graph.json (generated, but the diff is the erosion signal → collapse, expandable).
.beads/issues.jsonl                        -diff linguist-generated=true merge=union
sdlc-devtools/docs/architecture/graph.json linguist-generated=true
